name: Caspur Zoomies
description: $Caspur — the wildest cat on BNB! Chasing bags, not mice. A money-loving feline on a mission for financial freedom this super cycle, Caspur Zoomies brings humor, nostalgia, and community energy to the Binance Smart Chain. Inspired by a forgotten black-and-white cartoon cat who’s now clawing his way back to fame, $Caspur celebrates meme culture and the thrill of collective success. Powered by its playful holders and creative storytelling, the project aims to turn every “zoomie” into a step toward the next big meme legacy.
